flowchart LR
    INTENT[Intent: WAITING]

    INTENT --> RESUME[POST /intents/:id/resume]
    INTENT --> CTRL[PATCH /intents/:id/controls]
    INTENT --> POL[PATCH /intents/:id/policy]

    RESUME --> GATE{policy grants\nallow resume?}
    CTRL --> CASCK{policy_generation\nmatches?}
    POL --> CASCK

    GATE -->|yes| EXEC[resume execution]
    GATE -->|no| DENY[403 Forbidden]

    CASCK -->|yes| APPLY[apply delta]
    CASCK -->|no| CONFLICT[409 Conflict\nretry with fresh generation]
    APPLY --> EXEC
